</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong>Mohammad Farhan</strong> teaches English at Jamia Millia Islamia, New Delhi, India. He’s a regular contributor to various reputed newspapers and literary magazines including <em>Wasafiri</em>, among others.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
